      <p class="lead hero-subtitle">The air traffic controller mortgage — how controllers qualify for home loans. Federal pay scales look simple on paper. In practice, an ATC's real pay can be 40–80% above the published GS number once you add locality, Sunday premium, night differential, holiday pay, and Controller Incentive Pay. Most lenders use the published number. We use the real number.</p>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/purchase-inquiry/" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Get your air traffic controller mortgage pre-approval</a>
        <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/schedule-call" class="btn btn-secondary btn-large">Talk to Our Team about your air traffic controller mortgage</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-trust">
        <span class="trust-dot"></span>
        <span>NMLS #1072866</span>
        <span>·</span>
        <span>Specialist in aviation-industry &amp; variable-income mortgages</span>
      </div>
        </div>
        <figure class="hero-image">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/33608251/pexels-photo-33608251.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200" alt="Modern airport control tower bathed in sunset light over an airfield" width="1200" height="1500" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/1200x1500/0A0E1A/E8EEFF/png?text=ATC+Tower+at+Sunset';">
